Rating: 3
Okay, I didn't do the recipe EXACTLY as called for, but it still turned out well! I ended up using frozen white corn and frozen haricot verts and I didn't end up using the pesto...just salt and pepper and the taste was really good. The meal was simple and relatively inexpensive to make. I like meat so this was a good choice for two people...plus you can add more veggies if you need to.

